import { Drafts, Inbox, Send } from '@mui/icons-material'
import { Box, Divider, List, ListItem, ListItemButton, ListItemIcon, ListItemText, ListSubheader } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const LeftBar = () => {
  return (
    <Box flex={1} alignItems="center" justifyContent="space-between" sx={{ display: { xs: "none", sm: "block" } }}>
      <nav aria-label="main mailbox folders">
        <List>
          <ListItem disablePadding>
            <ListItemButton>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <Inbox />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Inbox" />
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
          <ListItem disablePadding>
            <ListItemButton>
              <ListItemIcon>
                <Drafts />
              </ListItemIcon>
              <ListItemText primary="Drafts" />
            </ListItemButton>
          </ListItem>
        </List>
      </nav>
      <Divider />
    </Box >
  )
}

export default LeftBar
